Two ways to install d3 ->
1) type "npm install d3"
   -- This will install the latest version of d3
   -- To install a specific version type "npm install d3@5.16.0" 
   -- To find the available versions visit - https://github.com/d3/d3/releases
2) In package.json add ("d3": "^5.16.0") as a dependency
   and then type "npm install" in command line - For mac and linux users, you might type sudo npm install in some className
-------------------------------
Import D3: import * as d3 from 'd3';
-------------------------------